  <h2>Do‚Äôs & Don‚Äôts During Flood</h2>

  <h3>‚úî Do‚Äôs</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Move immediately to higher ground.</li>
    <li>Turn off electricity and gas supply before evacuating.</li>
    <li>Take your emergency kit and essential medicines.</li>
    <li>Help children, elderly, and persons with disabilities.</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>‚ùå Don‚Äôts</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Do NOT walk or drive through moving floodwater.</li>
    <li>Do NOT touch electric poles, transformers, or wet wires.</li>
    <li>Do NOT drink untreated water.</li>
    <li>Do NOT spread rumors or panic.</li>
  </ul>
</article>

